## building a chroot

### preparing a ruby for the chroot

Grab a Ruby and .configure --prefix=/ruby; make; sudo make install

### building

    sudo ./bin/build.rb [-v] {target_dir}

if you've build the target Ruby in /ruby :

    sudo ./bin/build.rb -v --rp /ruby target

